The paper discusses a novel compression method for deep neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). However, since the focus is on compressing deep neural networks for object recognition, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG and cs.CV, followed by cs.AI and cs.NE. The least likely sub-category is cs.DC, as the paper does not discuss distributed or parallel computing.
